    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">花</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>によう<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">似</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">に</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>た<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">姿</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">すがた</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をば、<lb />
なんの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">花</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>かと<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">問</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">と</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>われると<lb />
すぐには<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">返答</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">へんと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">困</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>るけど。<lb />
<lb />
ただ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">微笑</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほほえ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>みてものいわず、<lb />
うす<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">青白</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あおしろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>き<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夢</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">世</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、<lb />
いまは<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">幻</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まぼろし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>と<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">浮</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">う</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>かぶかな。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">花</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にいろいろあるけれど、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">燃</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">も</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>える<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">紅</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>い<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">花</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>でない。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">冷</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>たい<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">白</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>い<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">花</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>でない。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夏</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はまだ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">浅</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あさ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>く、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">色</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">淡</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あわ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>く、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">紫陽花</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あじさい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">咲</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>くころに、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">私</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">わたし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">姉</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ねえ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>さん<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">思</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>い<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">出</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">だ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>す。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
